query:
with unscraped_ids as (
            select
                distinct public_id
            from
                smart_scout

            except

            select
                distinct ss.public_id
            from
                smart_scout ss
                join smart_scout_job ssj on ssj.smart_scout_id = ss.id
        )
        select
            ss.id,
            ss.name
        from
            smart_scout ss
            join unscraped_ids ui on ui.public_id = ss.public_id
        where
            ss.name is not null
        order by random()
        limit $1
